criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        All patients with acute critical illness who are eligible for admission to ICU during the
        study period

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients under the age of 16;

          2. Pregnant and parturient women;

          3. Patients who planned to be admitted to the department for surgery and transferred the
             next day after evaluation;

          4. Patients admitted to the department and diagnosed with sepsis;

          5. Patients with ICU stay less than 24 hours;
